				<div class="card">
					<div class="card-body">
						<h4 class="card-title">Who Are We?</h4>
						<p class="card-text">
						Members of robotics team Westside Boiler Invasion participate year-round in FIRST速 related activities, whether it be robot-building practice, website coding for team promotion, or outreach events to promote FIRST速 robotics and STEM education. This helps to not only prepare students for FIRST速 Robotics Competitions (FRC), but it also helps to familiarize team members with the principles of FIRST速.	
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
